Add X1830 support in "ingenic_pinconf_get()", so that it can read the
configuration of X1830 SoC correctly.

Fixes: d7da2a1e4e08 ("pinctrl: Ingenic: Add pinctrl driver for X1830.")
Cc: <stable@vger.kernel.org>
